Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:05.10,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,So you're Nico's parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.10,0:00:06.44,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,You look just like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:09.62,RiskySubs,Nico's Father,0,0,0,,I am the top officer at Universe Patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.62,0:00:11.62,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Dang, Nico's got it good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,0:00:13.52,RiskySubs,Nico's Mother,0,0,0,,I want to see Nico again...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.90,0:00:15.62,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Oh, we doing a flashback?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:18.00,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Don't let it run too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:20.86,RiskySubs,Nico's Father,0,0,0,,We visited the Dark World
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.86,0:00:22.48,RiskySubs,Nico's Father,0,0,0,,to stop Dark Kuromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.85,0:00:25.40,RiskySubs,Nico's Father,0,0,0,,But she was more tricky than I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:27.19,RiskySubs,Nico's Father,0,0,0,,and she stole my MM.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.48,0:00:29.94,RiskySubs,Nico's Mother,0,0,0,,In order to get Nico out,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.94,0:00:32.65,RiskySubs,Nico's Mother,0,0,0,,I quickly gave him my MM,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.65,0:00:34.35,RiskySubs,Nico's Mother,0,0,0,,and he ran off with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.98,0:00:38.06,RiskySubs,Nico's Father,0,0,0,,Ever since then, we've been trapped here,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.06,0:00:40.60,RiskySubs,Nico's Father,0,0,0,,constantly looking for a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.06,0:00:40.60,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}I can't stop focusing on his fluffy 'stache...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:42.06,RiskySubs,Nico's Father,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, fluffy what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.06,0:00:43.77,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Uh, forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:46.77,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,So this MM wasn't Nico's then?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:50.40,RiskySubs,Nico's Mother,0,0,0,,Nico doesn't have one,\Nsince he's an apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:53.77,RiskySubs,Nico's Father,0,0,0,,We don't want him running the risk\Nof interfering with other worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.77,0:00:54.65,RiskySubs,Nico's Parents,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.65,0:00:55.52,RiskySubs,Nico's Parents,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.77,0:00:57.35,RiskySubs,Nico's Mother,0,0,0,,It's my MM!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:00:58.44,RiskySubs,Nico's Father,0,0,0,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.44,0:01:00.69,RiskySubs,Nico's Father,0,0,0,,We found this world's key.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.69,0:01:03.10,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Jeez, it really does look like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:05.23,RiskySubs,Nico's Father,0,0,0,,I'll tap it, so please return my MM.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:07.80,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Sweet! I'm on my way, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.80,0:01:08.60,RiskySubs,MM,0,0,0,,{\i1}Universe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.60,0:01:09.31,RiskySubs,Nico's Father,0,0,0,,Wait!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.31,0:01:10.42,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:11.14,RiskySubs,Nico's Father,0,0,0,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:12.76,RiskySubs,MM,0,0,0,,{\i1}Universe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.35,0:01:14.02,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Tap!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.02,0:01:15.14,RiskySubs,MM,0,0,0,,{\i1}Universe!
